Title: bashburn.tcz
Description: Text mode CD/DVD burning and audio converting utility.
Version: 3.0
Author: Anders Linden and others
Original-site: http://bashburn.dose.se/
Copying-policy: GPL
Size: 74K
Extension_by: Jason W
Comments: Default CD/DVD drive is set to /dev/hdc
  in the default config file so bashburn should work out of the box
  for most users. Use the setup option to change this
  and other defaults. Reloading the extension upon reboot will not
  overwrite an existing configuration.
  Depends= cdrtools.tcz, ncurses-utils.tcz, coreutils.tcz lame.tcz, 
  mpg123.tcz, flac.tcz, 
  dvd+-rwtools.tcz, ogg-vorbis.tcz, cdrdao.tcz, cdparanoia.tcz
